<view class="container"><view class="header"><view class="back-icon avatar ai-avatar" bindtap="{{b}}"><image src="{{a}}"></image></view><view class="title">AI旅游助手</view><view class="more-icon" bindtap="{{d}}"><image src="{{c}}"></image></view></view><scroll-view scroll-y class="chat-container" scroll-top="{{h}}" scroll-with-animation scroll-into-view="{{i}}"><view class="message ai-message" id="msg-0"><view class="avatar ai-avatar"><image src="{{e}}" mode="aspectFill"></image></view><view class="message-content"><text>欢迎使用AI旅游助手！我可以帮您规划完美的海岛之旅。您可以选择以下热门选项，或直接告诉我您的需求。</text><view class="category-container"><view wx:for="{{f}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="c" class="category-item" bindtap="{{item.d}}"><image src="{{item.a}}" mode="aspectFit"></image><text>{{item.b}}</text></view></view></view></view><block wx:for="{{g}}" wx:for-item="msg" wx:key="x"><view wx:if="{{msg.a}}" class="message user-message" id="{{msg.d}}"><view class="avatar user-avatar"><image src="{{msg.b}}"></image></view><view class="message-content"><text>{{msg.c}}</text></view></view><view wx:else class="message ai-message" id="{{msg.w}}"><view class="avatar ai-avatar"><image src="{{msg.e}}" mode="aspectFill"></image></view><view class="message-content"><image wx:if="{{msg.f}}" class="response-image" src="{{msg.g}}" mode="widthFix"></image><rich-text wx:if="{{msg.h}}" class="message-content" nodes="{{msg.i}}"></rich-text><view wx:if="{{msg.j}}" class="itinerary-container"><view class="itinerary-title">{{msg.k}}</view><view class="itinerary-section"><text class="section-title">行程安排:</text><view wx:for="{{msg.l}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="c" class="itinerary-item"><text class="time">{{item.a}}:</text><rich-text class="detail" nodes="{{item.b}}"></rich-text></view></view><view wx:if="{{msg.m}}" class="recommendations"><text class="section-title">推荐商家:</text><view wx:for="{{msg.n}}" wx:for-item="rec" wx:key="c" class="recommendation-item"><text class="place">{{rec.a}}:</text><text class="description">{{rec.b}}</text></view></view><view wx:if="{{msg.o}}" class="price-container"><view class="price-info"><text class="price">¥ {{msg.p}}</text><text class="price-details">{{msg.q}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{msg.r}}" class="discount"> 优惠·¥{{msg.s}}元 </view></view><button wx:if="{{msg.t}}" class="confirm-button" bindtap="{{msg.v}}">确认行程并购买</button></view></view></view></block></scroll-view><view class="input-container"><view class="add-icon" bindtap="{{j}}"><text class="iconfont"></text></view><input class="message-input" type="text" placeholder="输入您的需求" bindconfirm="{{k}}" value="{{l}}" bindinput="{{m}}"/><view class="send-icon" bindtap="{{n}}"><text class="iconfont"></text></view></view></view>